{"tid":1422673,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好想發夢睇到巴打們大大力錫佢春袋","createTime":"2019-08-06T11:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T10:27:58.000Z","uid":90290,"like":125,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e16a4ae0f3a08294feb75489a86b50c538b97b0a","tid":1422673,"uid":90290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:36:42.000Z","msg":"對唔住我係一個唔敢上前線既絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有個小小請求比前線勇武巴打們<br />\n尋日有睇到片大家好落力去圍毆落單白衫/狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係既我係睇到好爽既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我內心竟然係大叫緊:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除褲除褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />影相影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家諗返當日天水圍個女仔比人拉個陣發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身為年紀相近既女仔，我冇絲打既心理狀態咁好<br />\n如果個日既事發生係我身上我一定嬲到仆街以後見到狗都會想佢當眾出醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家發夢捉到落單狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">除褲<br />\n影JJ<br />\n大大力錫佢春袋<br />\n影大頭<br />\n起底<br />\n貼全街</span><br />\n唔知佢有咩感受呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">以上只係發白日夢如有雷同實屬夢境成真</span>"},{"pid":"8fbbad13df946a2e6b5df5e931baa63cd75c32f8","tid":1422673,"uid":274180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93eb46b85194a54f9cf4073301b1efd6700a66a5","tid":1422673,"uid":90290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fbbad13df946a2e6b5df5e931baa63cd75c32f8","tid":1422673,"uid":274180,